'''酯的热裂'''是含β氢的[[酯|酯]]在高温真空中进行[[裂解|裂解]]，生成相应[[羧酸|羧酸]]和[[烯烃|烯烃]]的反应。该反应属于[[Ei消除反应|Ei消除反应]]，只适用于对热稳定的化合物。

[[File:Ester_pyrolysis.png|thumb]]在590°C分解为[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]和[[乙烯|乙烯]]。]]

例子有：
*以[[丙烯酸乙酯|丙烯酸乙酯]]590°C裂解合成[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]<ref>[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]], Coll. Vol. 3, p.30 ('''1955'''); Vol. 29, p.2 ('''1949'''). [http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0030.pdf Link] {{Wayback|url=http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV3P0030.pdf |date=20120207022453 }}</ref>
*以二乙酸戊二醇二酯575°C裂解合成[[1,4-戊二烯|1,4-戊二烯]]<ref>[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]], Coll. Vol. 4, p.746 ('''1963'''); Vol. 38, p.78 ('''1958'''). [http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV4P0746.pdf Link] {{Wayback|url=http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV4P0746.pdf |date=20120207022505 }}</ref>
*酯700°C热裂合成[[环丁烯|环丁烯]]环系<ref>[[Organic_Syntheses|Organic Syntheses]], Coll. Vol. 5, p.235 ('''1973'''); Vol. 43, p.17 ('''1963'''). [http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV5P0235.pdf Link] {{Wayback|url=http://orgsynth.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV5P0235.pdf |date=20120207022521 }}</ref>

